race.description: Thank You Len Tozer Country Magic Showcase Handicap
race.comment: THE EYES HAVE IT (12) rewarded for her consistency at start eleven when taken to the front for a comfortable win over 1400m at Nowra. Can get the job done again from the low gate. SNOWY (4) sound return when covering ground early before closing late for a narrow second over 1200m at Canberra in C2 class. Has won at this course and proven second-up. Leading player. EAST HARLEM (9) excellent run at Bathurst two-back when third to Scopics, before stalking the pace when a tidy fifth over 1300m at Dubbo. Proven at the trip and gets his chance. CINEPHILE (13) failed to back up from the wide gate when a plugging tenth over this trip at Wangaratta. Gets a better set-up today and placed here.
